item.description: It's Football Season.Come join us Sunday for the PATS vs the NY JETS at 4pm followed by Karaoke at 8pm at the Rosebud.It's a throwback game with the Pats wearing their throwback uniforms, so come on down to the Rosebud and throwback a few of your own and kick out a few throwback song from the day What can be better Patriots Football blasted on all the screens throughout the Bar,kicking the NY Jets all over the field, watch and listen to all the action and big plays. Then stick around and rock the house or get ready to be rocked by all the talent.......
item.name: Patriots vs Jets followed by Karaoke Sunday @ The Rosebud
